        <h1>
            <span style="color:black">Clinical Psychology - The Relationship between the mind & human behavior</span>
        </h1>
        <a href="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-vector/male-character-psychotherapist-appointment-psychologist-talking-1837184797?utm_campaign=image&utm_medium=googleimages&utm_source=iptc"
