            which include:

        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.psychfinder.co.uk/london/psychologist">Psychfinder</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.bps.org.uk/find-psychologist">The British Psychological Society</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.psychotherapy.org.uk/find-a-therapist/?Distance=10">UK Council for
                    Psychotherapy</a></li>
            <li><a
                    href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/check-practitioners/practitioner/clinical-psychologist">Professional
                    Standards Authority for Health & Social Care</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://findmypsychologist.co.uk/">Find My Psychologist</a></li>
        </ul>

        There are other resources, which can all be found via Google or
        other search engine.
        </p>
